1. *Omiljeni* mi je film bio Star Wars. (My favorite movie was Star Wars.)

2. On je svojoj sestri doneo njen *omiljeni* sladoled. (He bought his sister her favorite ice cream.)

3. Ovo je moja *omiljena* knjiga. (This is my favorite book.)

4. *Omiljene* mi boje su plava i zelena. (My favorite colors are blue and green.)

5. Ona je kupila svojoj majci *omiljenu* haljinu. (She bought her mother her favorite dress.)

6. Njegov *omiljeni* sport je bili tenis. (His favorite sport was tennis.)